        "synopsis": {
            "value": "Lobby manager Tu Xiao Ning is on probation at Huayuan Tower, while Ji Yu Heng, a rising star on the 17th floor, shares her dream of marriage. Once childhood friends, their paths cross again as Yu Heng becomes Xiao Ning’s boss. To Xiao Ning, Yu Heng is the ideal partner; to Yu Heng, Xiao Ning is his destined choice. Despite workplace challenges and their new roles as colleagues and newlyweds, they navigate\n\nthe complexities of love, marriage, and ambition, rediscovering the meaning of life together in the process.",
